### Get all student schedules

GET http://localhost:8080/api/student-schedules HTTP/1.1


### Get student schedule with id 1

GET http://localhost:8080/api/student-schedules/1 HTTP/1.1


### Delete student schedule 2

DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/student-schedules/2 HTTP/1.1


### Verify remaining student schedules

GET http://localhost:8080/api/student-schedules HTTP/1.1
